  <script>
   if (!Array.prototype.indexOf)
	{
	  Array.prototype.indexOf = function(elt /*, from*/)
	  {
	    var len = this.length >>> 0;

	    var from = Number(arguments[1]) || 0;
	    from = (from < 0)
	         ? Math.ceil(from)
	         : Math.floor(from);
	    if (from < 0)
	      from += len;

	    for (; from < len; from++)
	    {
	      if (from in this &&
	          this[from] === elt)
	        return from;
	    }
	    return -1;
	  }
	}
  </script>
